Interface MEMEDataSource

All Superinterfaces:
Connection
All Known Subinterfaces:
MIDDataSource, MRDDataSource
All Known Implementing Classes:
MEMEConnection, MIDConnection, MRDConnection
public interface MEMEDataSource
extends Connection

Represents a connection to a source of MEME data. Typically a MID or MRD.

Author:
MEME Group
